{"id": 799, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都怎么委婉地说再见？", "description": "一个深谙成人世界语言系统的我。（题图来自：Janne Livonen）", "record_count": 4899, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016070313004587LWu0PhvBYOeXTC.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-16T11:47:08Z", "options": [{"id": 50862, "content": "嗯嗯，晚安。   么么哒??", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475982}, {"id": 51201, "content": "退下吧，朕累了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470838}, {"id": 52737, "content": "有点事有空聊。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401788}, {"id": 50690, "content": "完", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456607}, {"id": 50691, "content": "再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462491}, {"id": 51203, "content": "等一会再联系啊我这边有点事", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478617}, {"id": 50692, "content": "我先吃个饭，回聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475285}, {"id": 54020, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335237}, {"id": 50693, "content": "青山常在，绿水常流，好汉我们有缘再会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367798}, {"id": 50694, "content": "改天请你吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256207}, {"id": 50695, "content": "手机没电了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475300}, {"id": 50696, "content": "跪安吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205108}, {"id": 50697, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475301}, {"id": 51209, "content": "不说了有点困了诶，晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478494}, {"id": 50698, "content": "突然有点事，下次我再找你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475315}, {"id": 52234, "content": "拉黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479052}, {"id": 50699, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475322}, {"id": 50700, "content": "哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182838GKD3a8O6LkzSYVrA.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475322}, {"id": 50701, "content": "好的，回聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475328}, {"id": 51725, "content": "早睡 好梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436707}, {"id": 50702, "content": "我去拉泡屎昂~", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461123}, {"id": 50703, "content": "你走…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41805}, {"id": 50704, "content": "WANAN=Wo Ai Ni, Ai Ni. \"我爱你，爱你”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475339}, {"id": 50705, "content": "我有点困了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331480}, {"id": 50706, "content": "ciao", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355977}, {"id": 50708, "content": "先去开会了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473685}, {"id": 50710, "content": "着火了！地震了！洪水来了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417958}, {"id": 50711, "content": "等一哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475354}, {"id": 50712, "content": "有点事，回聊哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362855}, {"id": 54552, "content": "把手机拿远", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494956}, {"id": 50713, "content": "...", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475360}, {"id": 51225, "content": "我妈妈叫我吃饭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478779}, {"id": 50715, "content": "“好了，早点休息哈，晚安”或者什么也不说，就自动拜拜了，", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307916}, {"id": 50716, "content": "恩", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475370}, {"id": 50717, "content": "…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471752}, {"id": 50718, "content": "滚!", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307055}, {"id": 50719, "content": "886", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475388}, {"id": 50720, "content": "好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 80679}, {"id": 52512, "content": "啊 天都黑了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485719}, {"id": 50721, "content": "呵呵～", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313765}, {"id": 50722, "content": "哦哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475387}, {"id": 50978, "content": "下次再聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444689}, {"id": 50723, "content": "再见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463858}, {"id": 50979, "content": "吃饭去了哈，先不说了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 455117}, {"id": 50725, "content": "发个。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475400}, {"id": 50726, "content": "88", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475401}, {"id": 50982, "content": "对不起，有人找我，回聊哈，拜拜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476836}, {"id": 50727, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139557}, {"id": 52520, "content": "我还有事。。", "image": null, 